name: Rank-Up-Magic Omniforce
text:
(This card is always treated as an "Omni" Spell Card.)
Target 1 "Omni" Xyz Monster you control; Special Summon from your Extra Deck, 1 "Omni" Xyz Monster that is 1 Rank higher, by using it and this card as the Xyz Materials. (This is treated as an Xyz Summon. Transfer its materials to the Summoned monster.)
You can only activate 1 "Rank-Up-Magic Omniforce" once per turn.
